response:
```java
@RestController
@RequestMapping("/api")
public class HealthController {

    @Autowired
    private DataSource dataSource;

    @Autowired
    private StringRedisTemplate redisTemplate;

    @GetMapping("/health")
    public ResponseEntity<Map<String, Object>> health() {
        Map<String, Object> status = new LinkedHashMap<>();

        // DB ping
        try (Connection conn = dataSource.getConnection()) {
            conn.isValid(1);
            status.put("db", "ok");
        } catch (Exception e) {
            status.put("db", "fail: " + e.getMessage());
        }

        // Redis ping
        try {
            String pong = redisTemplate.getConnectionFactory()
                .getConnection().ping();
            status.put("redis", "ok".equals(pong.toLowerCase()) || "pong".equals(pong.toLowerCase()) ? "ok" : pong);
        } catch (Exception e) {
            status.put("redis", "fail: " + e.getMessage());
        }

        boolean healthy = status.values().stream().allMatch("ok"::equals);
        status.put("status", healthy ? "UP" : "DOWN");

        return ResponseEntity
            .status(healthy ? 200 : 503)
            .body(status);
    }
}
```

**의존성** (`build.gradle` 또는 `pom.xml`에 이미 있어야 함):
- `spring-boot-starter-data-redis`
- `spring-boot-starter-jdbc` (또는 JPA)

**응답 예시:**
```json
{
  "db": "ok",
  "redis": "ok",
  "status": "UP"
}
```
DB나 Redis 중 하나라도 실패하면 `503`을 반환합니다.
